OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776416752
OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,7,Fannounced a 10-day ceasefire after
OL,8,Ftalks with the Lebanese president and
OL,9,Fthe Israeli prime minister.
OL,11,FTrump announced in a Truth Social post
OL,12,Fon Thursday afternoon that the leaders
OL,13,Fagreed to a truce starting at 5pm EST,
OL,14,F10pm UK time.
OL,16,FLebanese Prime Minister Joseph Aoun
OL,17,Fsaid he "welcomes" the announcement,
OL,18,F"which is a central Lebanese demand we
OL,19,Fhave pursued since the first day of
OL,20,Fthe war, and was our primary goal in
OL,21,Fthe Washington meeting on Tuesday".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
