OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776416752
OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,FPresident Trump wrote: "These two
OL,7,FLeaders have agreed that in order to
OL,8,Fachieve PEACE between their Countries,
OL,9,Fthey will formally begin a 10 Day
OL,10,FCEASEFIRE at 5 P.M. EST."
OL,12,F"I have directed Vice President JD
OL,13,FVance and Secretary of State Rubio,
OL,14,Ftogether with the Chairman of the
OL,15,FJoint Chiefs of Staff, Dan Razin'
OL,16,FCaine, to work with Israel and Lebanon
OL,17,Fto achieve a Lasting PEACE," he
OL,18,Fcontinued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776416752
OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,F"It has been my Honor to solve 9 Wars
OL,7,Facross the World, and this will be my
OL,8,F10th, so let's, GET IT DONE!," the
OL,9,Fpost concluded.
OL,11,FThe announcement comes after talks
OL,12,Fbetween Lebanon and Israel had
OL,13,Fappeared to stall earlier in the day.
OL,15,FLebanon and Israel held their first
OL,16,Fdirect diplomatic talks in decades on
OL,17,FTuesday in Washington after more than
OL,18,Fa month of war between Israel and the
OL,19,FIran-backed Hezbollah militant group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
