OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe US president also posted that he
OL,12,Fwould invite both leaders to the White
OL,13,FHouse "for the first meaningful talks
OL,14,Fbetween Israel and Lebanon since 1983".
OL,16,F"Both sides want to see PEACE, and I
OL,17,Fbelieve that will happen, quickly!,"
OL,18,Fhe added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
