PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776416752
OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,FThe Lebanese President Joseph Aoun had
OL,7,Freportedly refused to speak to Israeli
OL,8,FPrime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu, but
OL,9,FPresident Aoun subsequently spoke to
OL,10,Fthe US president on the phone and
OL,11,Fthanked him for his "efforts ... in
OL,12,Fexerting to reach a ceasefire".
OL,14,FIsraeli strikes on Lebanon had
OL,15,Fcontinued while talks were underway,
OL,16,Fincluding the destruction of a key
OL,17,Fbridge over the Litani River and
OL,18,Fattacks that killed rescue workers on
OL,19,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776416752
OL,3,CTrump says Israel and Lebanon agree to
OL,4,C10-day ceasefire
OL,6,FIsrael has insisted throughout that
OL,7,Fits strikes are aimed at targets they
OL,8,Fsay are connected with Hezbollah,
OL,9,Fwhich is a designated terrorist
OL,10,Forganisation in at least 28 countries.
OL,12,FMore than 2,100 people have been
OL,13,Fkilled in Lebanon since the start of
OL,14,Fthe latest conflict with Israel.
OL,16,FThursday's announcement came as
OL,17,Fdiplomatic efforts to end the war
OL,18,Fcontinued across the Middle East, with
OL,19,Fleaders from Pakistan visiting Iran
OL,20,Fand Saudi Arabia to try to broker an
OL,21,Fextension of the ceasefire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
